tle=\"previous in cs.SD (accesskey p)\" rel=\"nofollow\">&lt;&nbsp;prev</a>\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"is-hidden-mobile\">&nbsp; | &nbsp;</span>    <span class=\"arrow\">\n      <a class=\"abs-button next-url\" href=\"/prevnext?id=2607.12706&amp;function=next&amp;context=cs.SD\" accesskey=\"n\"\n         title=\"next in cs.SD (accesskey n)\"  rel=\"nofollow\">next&nbsp;&gt;</a>\n    </span><br/>\n  </div><div class=\"list\">\n    <a class=\"abs-button abs-button-grey abs-button-small context-new\" href=\"/list/cs.SD/new\"  rel=\"nofollow\">new</a>\n    <span class=\"is-hidden-mobile\"> | </span>\n    <a class=\"abs-button abs-button-grey abs-button-small context-recent\" href=\"/list/cs.SD/recent\" rel=\"nofollow\">recent</a>\n    <span class=\"is-hidden-mobile\"> | </span><a class=\"abs-button abs-button-grey abs-button-small context-id\" href=\"/list/cs.SD/2026-07\" rel=\"nofollow\">2026-07</a>\n  </div><div class=\"abs-switch-cat\">\n    Change to browse by:\n    <div class=\"switch context-change\">", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "d13fb9a8-e7bc-4e7d-9598-28f6d475ab98", "uuid": "81797798-3e00-4038-a5ca-ff3553cdcbe3", "timestamp": "2026-07-15T07:17:37.005Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head><script>document.documentElement.classList.add('js');</script>  <title>[2607.12706v1] AutoSIFT: Automatic Style Sifting for Controllable Speech Generation with Arbitrary Style Infilling</title>\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"/static/browse/0.3.4/images/icons/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"/static/browse/0.3.4/images/icons/favicon-32x32.png\">\n  <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"/static/browse/0.3.4/images/icons/favicon-16x16.png\">\n  <link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/static/browse/0.3.4/images/icons/site.webmanif